[
  {
    "text": "At 14.7 hertz, the number fills Voss's monitor like a diagnosis.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "He transcribes it onto the whiteboard in red marker and steps back.",
    "start": 5.16,
    "end": 8.06
  },
  {
    "text": "The Neanderthal runes resonated in for sound, below human hearing, below most human perception",
    "start": 9.0,
    "end": 14.14
  },
  {
    "text": "entirely.",
    "start": 14.14,
    "end": 14.72
  },
  {
    "text": "But the crystal lattice in the Neanderthal tissue responds to it like a tuning fork,",
    "start": 15.22,
    "end": 18.94
  },
  {
    "text": "which means if he generates the inverse frequency, the destructive interference pattern, the",
    "start": 19.54,
    "end": 24.3
  },
  {
    "text": "crystal lattice should destabilize.",
    "start": 24.3,
    "end": 26.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Should.",
    "start": 26.86,
    "end": 27.28
  },
  {
    "text": "The word bothers him.",
    "start": 27.9,
    "end": 29.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Shurred is not will.",
    "start": 30.06,
    "end": 30.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Shurred is a hypothesis.",
    "start": 31.36,
    "end": 32.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Voss rewires the sonic emitter with copper stripped from a destroyed drone.",
    "start": 33.48,
    "end": 36.64
  },
  {
    "text": "He solders connections by hand.",
    "start": 37.4,
    "end": 38.82
  },
  {
    "text": "The joints are ugly.",
    "start": 39.52,
    "end": 40.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Functional.",
    "start": 41.14,
    "end": 41.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka watches from the doorway.",
    "start": 42.5,
    "end": 43.72
  },
  {
    "text": "She does not ask if it will work.",
    "start": 44.44,
    "end": 45.7
  },
  {
    "text": "She asks how long until it is ready.",
    "start": 46.28,
    "end": 47.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Voss says six hours.",
    "start": 48.92,
    "end": 49.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka says they have four.",
    "start": 50.64,
    "end": 51.66
  },
  {
    "text": "She turns and walks out.",
    "start": 52.4,
    "end": 53.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Voss picks up the sawdowing iron again.",
    "start": 54.52,
    "end": 56.06
  },
  {
    "text": "His hands are shaking now, not from fear.",
    "start": 56.9,
    "end": 59.06
  },
  {
    "text": "From thirty hours without sleep in the knowledge that four thousand people on the ridge behind",
    "start": 59.76,
    "end": 63.7
  },
  {
    "text": "him are counting on a frequency he calculated from a dead aliens arm.",
    "start": 63.7,
    "end": 66.94
  },
  {
    "text": "He solders faster.",
    "start": 67.74,
    "end": 68.62
  },
  {
    "text": "The emitter hums.",
    "start": 69.46,
    "end": 70.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Fourteen point seven hertz.",
    "start": 70.78,
    "end": 71.94
  },
  {
    "text": "The inverse.",
    "start": 72.44,
    "end": 73.02
  },
  {
    "text": "The antidote.",
    "start": 73.62,
    "end": 74.26
  },
  {
    "text": "He hopes.",
    "start": 74.82,
    "end": 75.46
  }
]